# ==========================================
# CLOUDFLARE PAGES PROXY REWRITES (_redirects)
# ==========================================
# Routes all /api/* requests from the Cloudflare Pages static frontend
# to the Express backend server deployed on Render.com.
# Cloudflare Pages proxies with HTTP 200 to avoid CORS and 405 errors.
/api/*  https://pixelisolate-backend.onrender.com/api/:splat  200
